<taxonomicName authority="(Sawai Singh &amp; Gill)" authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Sawai Singh &amp; Gill" baseAuthorityYear="2011" box="[373,808,1866,1889]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Ianagallia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="79" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bifurcata">
<emphasis box="[373,577,1867,1889]" italics="true" pageId="79" pageNumber="80">Ianagallia bifurcata</emphasis>
(Sawai Singh &amp; Gill)
</taxonomicName>
: 391. Head and thorax; 392. Face; 393. Male genital capsule, lateral view; 394. Style, dorsal view; 395. Connective, anterodorsal view; 396, 399. Aedeagus, lateral view, variations; 397, 398. Ventral process of aedeagus, posterior view, variations in branching.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="80.[151,1436,151,573]" pageId="80" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,376,151,176]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="80" pageNumber="81" reason="1">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Pygofer simple, caudal margin rather truncate. Styles typical of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kirkaldy. It" authorityYear="1903" box="[1092,1166,153,176]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Igerna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="80" pageNumber="81" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1092,1166,153,176]" italics="true" pageId="80" pageNumber="81">Igerna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Connective sclerotized and pigmented, longer than wide, lateral margins excavated. Aedeagus complex, stout basally, with ventral platelike apodeme having distal median acuminate process; aedeagal shaft with pair of basal processes directed caudally, shaft slender, with pair of lateral subapical teeth, at base of ventral apodeme and base of aedeagus with spines; gonopore apical. Anal collar simple.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="80.[151,1436,151,573]" box="[199,954,332,356]" pageId="80" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,370,332,356]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="80" pageNumber="81" reason="1">Measurement.</emphasis>
Male 
<quantity box="[441,540,332,356]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.1" pageId="80" pageNumber="81" unit="mm" value="4.1">4.10 mm</quantity>
long and 
<quantity box="[652,751,332,356]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" pageId="80" pageNumber="81" unit="mm" value="1.3">1.30 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes.
</paragraph>
